subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which historical palace is located in Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर में किस घरचंद्रशेखवाल पर्यावरण का एक प्रमोजन है।
explanation_en:
Hawa Mahal is a popular astronomical tower located in Jaipur known for its beautiful architecture.
English Explanation:
Hawa Mahal is a popular astronomical tower located in Jaipur known for its beautiful architecture.
Hawa Mahal is a monument built by Maharaja Sawai Pratap Singh in the early 19th century.
It is a part of the City Palace complex and features intricate latticework and design.
Hawa Mahal stands at a height of around 100 feet and consists of 953 windows.
It is named after its unique ventilation system, which allows fresh air to flow through the building.
